      handlerMove in class GodCard

    • handlerBuild

      public boolean handlerBuild​(Model model, GodCardController controller, PlayerBuild build, Cell buildingCell)
      This method makes controls for the build. If the player has not already used the god power return false to make a standard built, if not check: - The worker used to built is the same of the first two actions - If he has already built the first time reset flags and return false for a standard build - If is the power built action, set model next phase and messages to move, set flags at true and call the controller increase level to make it returning true
      Overrides:
      handlerBuild in class GodCard
      Parameters:
      model - the play model
      controller - the play controller
      build - the message received by the view
      buildingCell - the cell where the player wants to build
      Returns:
      true if a different control is done else false
